While we're waiting for the next truck to appear
我们在等待第二辆卡车的时候

3
00:00:02,642 --> 00:00:05,997
some of the younger cowboys rope up a bull for practice
一些年轻的牛仔们抓了一匹公牛

4
00:00:06,047 --> 00:00:09,515
as the rodeo season is about to start.
来玩一个叫做Rodeo的游戏（牛仔骑术表演）

5
00:00:13,420 --> 00:00:19,240
Vanderley is a budding rodeo star and makes it look deceptively easy.
范德雷是一个骑术高手 他看起来轻松自如

6
00:00:41,120 --> 00:00:45,118
They just saddled up a rodeo show for themselves
他们只是自娱自乐

7
00:00:45,267 --> 00:00:49,683
and then some bright spark looked at me and said, 'oi, do you want to have a go?'
但一会他们便过来怂恿我 试试吧

8
00:00:54,687 --> 00:00:55,484
Hand in here.
抓住这儿

9
00:00:58,447 --> 00:00:59,480
OK, and then?
好的 然后呢

10
00:01:00,487 --> 00:01:01,476
Squeeze here?
夹紧这儿

11
00:01:03,007 --> 00:01:04,120
And squeeze here.
夹紧这儿

12
00:01:04,330 --> 00:01:08,200
And then just...
然后

13
00:01:08,247 --> 00:01:10,284
Well, just...stupid question, really, isn't it?
哈哈 真是愚蠢的问题

14
00:01:10,327 --> 00:01:13,716
What are you supposed to do? Grip, hold on and grip!
你建议我怎么做？抓紧绳子 抓紧就好

15
00:01:13,767 --> 00:01:15,564
Well, there you go.
好的 游戏开始

16
00:01:15,607 --> 00:01:17,279
OK, OK.
好的 好的

17
00:01:17,327 --> 00:01:18,806
Right, here?
腿放在这儿么

18
00:01:25,647 --> 00:01:28,205
And when I fall off, which I will...
那要是掉下来的话 那我会……

19
00:01:30,487 --> 00:01:32,364
Just let go. And fall, then...
别紧张 摔了就松绳子

20
00:01:45,847 --> 00:01:48,520
Ah, ah, ow!
哦

21
00:01:48,577 --> 00:01:49,761
That hurt!
好痛啊

22
00:01:50,807 --> 00:01:52,399


23
00:01:52,321 --> 00:01:53,476
Argh!
啊

24
00:01:55,327 --> 00:01:57,680
That properly hurt.
痛死我了

25
00:02:01,647 --> 00:02:05,276
That was about two seconds on the rodeo. Whoo!
在牛背上呆了大概2秒

26
00:02:09,807 --> 00:02:12,116
That hurt! Ow! My last day of being a cowboy.
太疼了 喔 作为牛仔的最后一天

27
00:02:12,167 --> 00:02:15,125
and I think... Good way to leave it, really.
这倒是一个完美的结局方式

28
00:02:15,167 --> 00:02:17,727
Leave it to the big boys, the real cowboys.
还是让真正的年轻牛仔们去玩吧

29
00:02:23,287 --> 00:02:26,359
